40static inline double
41dd_hi(const double2 a)
42{
43 return a.x[0];
44}
45
46static inline double
47dd_lo(const double2 a)
48{
49 return a.x[1];
50}
51
52static inline int
53dd_isfinite(const double2 a)
54{
55 return isfinite(a.x[0]);
56}
57
58static inline int
59dd_isinf(const double2 a)
60{
61 return isinf(a.x[0]);
62}
63
64static inline int
65dd_is_zero(const double2 a)
66{
67 return (a.x[0] == 0.0);
68}
69
70static inline int
71dd_is_one(const double2 a)
72{
73 return (a.x[0] == 1.0 && a.x[1] == 0.0);
74}
75
76static inline int
77dd_is_positive(const double2 a)
78{
79 return (a.x[0] > 0.0);
80}
81
82static inline int
83dd_is_negative(const double2 a)
84{
85 return (a.x[0] < 0.0);
86}

88/* Cast to double. */
89static inline double
90dd_to_double(const double2 a)
91{
92 return a.x[0];
93}
94
95/* Cast to int. */
96static inline int
97dd_to_int(const double2 a)
98{
99 return DD_STATIC_CAST(int, a.x[0]);
100}

102/*********** Equality and Other Comparisons ************/
103static inline int
104dd_comp(const double2 a, const double2 b)
105{
106 int cmp = two_comp(a: a.x[0], b: b.x[0]);
107 if (cmp == 0) {
108 cmp = two_comp(a: a.x[1], b: b.x[1]);
109 }
110 return cmp;
111}
112
113static inline int
114dd_comp_dd_d(const double2 a, double b)
115{
116 int cmp = two_comp(a: a.x[0], b);
117 if (cmp == 0) {
118 cmp = two_comp(a: a.x[1], b: 0);
119 }
120 return cmp;
121}
122
123static inline int
124dd_comp_d_dd(double a, const double2 b)
125{
126 int cmp = two_comp(a, b: b.x[0]);
127 if (cmp == 0) {
128 cmp = two_comp(a: 0.0, b: b.x[1]);
129 }
130 return cmp;
131}

135static inline double2
136dd_create(double hi, double lo)
137{
138 double2 ret = {{hi, lo}};
139 return ret;
140}
141
142static inline double2
143dd_zero(void)
144{
145 return DD_C_ZERO;
146}
147
148static inline double2
149dd_create_d(double hi)
150{
151 double2 ret = {{hi, 0.0}};
152 return ret;
153}
154
155static inline double2
156dd_create_i(int hi)
157{
158 double2 ret = {{DD_STATIC_CAST(double, hi), 0.0}};
159 return ret;
160}

162static inline double2
163dd_create_dp(const double *d)
164{
165 double2 ret = {{d[0], d[1]}};
166 return ret;

170/*********** Unary Minus ***********/
171static inline double2
172dd_neg(const double2 a)
173{
174 double2 ret = {{-a.x[0], -a.x[1]}};
175 return ret;
176}

178/*********** Rounding ************/
179/* Round to Nearest integer */
180static inline double2
181dd_nint(const double2 a)
182{
183 double hi = two_nint(d: a.x[0]);
184 double lo;
185
186 if (hi == a.x[0]) {
187 /* High word is an integer already. Round the low word.*/
188 lo = two_nint(d: a.x[1]);
189
190 /* Renormalize. This is needed if x[0] = some integer, x[1] = 1/2.*/
191 hi = quick_two_sum(a: hi, b: lo, err: &lo);
192 }
193 else {
194 /* High word is not an integer. */
195 lo = 0.0;
196 if (fabs(x: hi - a.x[0]) == 0.5 && a.x[1] < 0.0) {
197 /* There is a tie in the high word, consult the low word
198 to break the tie. */
199 hi -= 1.0; /* NOTE: This does not cause INEXACT. */
200 }
201 }
202
203 return dd_create(hi, lo);
204}
205
206static inline double2
207dd_floor(const double2 a)
208{
209 double hi = floor(x: a.x[0]);
210 double lo = 0.0;
211
212 if (hi == a.x[0]) {
213 /* High word is integer already. Round the low word. */
214 lo = floor(x: a.x[1]);
215 hi = quick_two_sum(a: hi, b: lo, err: &lo);
216 }
217
218 return dd_create(hi, lo);
219}
220
221static inline double2
222dd_ceil(const double2 a)
223{
224 double hi = ceil(x: a.x[0]);
225 double lo = 0.0;
226
227 if (hi == a.x[0]) {
228 /* High word is integer already. Round the low word. */
229 lo = ceil(x: a.x[1]);
230 hi = quick_two_sum(a: hi, b: lo, err: &lo);
231 }
232
233 return dd_create(hi, lo);
234}
235
236static inline double2
237dd_aint(const double2 a)
238{
239 return (a.x[0] >= 0.0) ? dd_floor(a) : dd_ceil(a);
240}
241
242/* Absolute value */
243static inline double2
244dd_abs(const double2 a)
245{
246 return (a.x[0] < 0.0 ? dd_neg(a) : a);
247}
248
249static inline double2
250dd_fabs(const double2 a)
251{
252 return dd_abs(a);
253}

256/*********** Normalizing ***********/
257/* double-double * (2.0 ^ expt) */
258static inline double2
259dd_ldexp(const double2 a, int expt)
260{
261 return dd_create(hi: ldexp(x: a.x[0], exponent: expt), lo: ldexp(x: a.x[1], exponent: expt));
262}
263
264static inline double2
265dd_frexp(const double2 a, int *expt)
266{
267// r"""return b and l s.t. 0.5<=|b|<1 and 2^l == a
268// 0.5<=|b[0]|<1.0 or |b[0]| == 1.0 and b[0]*b[1]<0
269// """
270 int exponent;
271 double man = frexp(x: a.x[0], exponent: &exponent);
272 double b1 = ldexp(x: a.x[1], exponent: -exponent);
273 if (fabs(x: man) == 0.5 && man * b1 < 0)
274 {
275 man *=2;
276 b1 *= 2;
277 exponent -= 1;
278 }
279 *expt = exponent;
280 return dd_create(hi: man, lo: b1);
281}

284/*********** Additions ************/
285static inline double2
286dd_add_d_d(double a, double b)
287{
288 double s, e;
289 s = two_sum(a, b, err: &e);
290 return dd_create(hi: s, lo: e);
291}
292
293static inline double2
294dd_add_dd_d(const double2 a, double b)
295{
296 double s1, s2;
297 s1 = two_sum(a: a.x[0], b, err: &s2);
298 s2 += a.x[1];
299 s1 = quick_two_sum(a: s1, b: s2, err: &s2);
300 return dd_create(hi: s1, lo: s2);
301}
302
303static inline double2
304dd_add_d_dd(double a, const double2 b)
305{
306 double s1, s2;
307 s1 = two_sum(a, b: b.x[0], err: &s2);
308 s2 += b.x[1];
309 s1 = quick_two_sum(a: s1, b: s2, err: &s2);
310 return dd_create(hi: s1, lo: s2);
311}
312
313static inline double2
314dd_ieee_add(const double2 a, const double2 b)
315{
316 /* This one satisfies IEEE style error bound,
317 due to K. Briggs and W. Kahan. */
318 double s1, s2, t1, t2;
319
320 s1 = two_sum(a: a.x[0], b: b.x[0], err: &s2);
321 t1 = two_sum(a: a.x[1], b: b.x[1], err: &t2);
322 s2 += t1;
323 s1 = quick_two_sum(a: s1, b: s2, err: &s2);
324 s2 += t2;
325 s1 = quick_two_sum(a: s1, b: s2, err: &s2);
326 return dd_create(hi: s1, lo: s2);
327}
328
329static inline double2
330dd_sloppy_add(const double2 a, const double2 b)
331{
332 /* This is the less accurate version ... obeys Cray-style
333 error bound. */
334 double s, e;
335
336 s = two_sum(a: a.x[0], b: b.x[0], err: &e);
337 e += (a.x[1] + b.x[1]);
338 s = quick_two_sum(a: s, b: e, err: &e);
339 return dd_create(hi: s, lo: e);
340}
341
342static inline double2
343dd_add(const double2 a, const double2 b)
344{
345 /* Always require IEEE-style error bounds */
346 return dd_ieee_add(a, b);
347}

349/*********** Subtractions ************/
350/* double-double = double - double */
351static inline double2
352dd_sub_d_d(double a, double b)
353{
354 double s, e;
355 s = two_diff(a, b, err: &e);
356 return dd_create(hi: s, lo: e);
357}
358
359static inline double2
360dd_sub(const double2 a, const double2 b)
361{
362 return dd_ieee_add(a, b: dd_neg(a: b));
363}
364
365static inline double2
366dd_sub_dd_d(const double2 a, double b)
367{
368 double s1, s2;
369 s1 = two_sum(a: a.x[0], b: -b, err: &s2);
370 s2 += a.x[1];
371 s1 = quick_two_sum(a: s1, b: s2, err: &s2);
372 return dd_create(hi: s1, lo: s2);
373}
374
375static inline double2
376dd_sub_d_dd(double a, const double2 b)
377{
378 double s1, s2;
379 s1 = two_sum(a, b: -b.x[0], err: &s2);
380 s2 -= b.x[1];
381 s1 = quick_two_sum(a: s1, b: s2, err: &s2);
382 return dd_create(hi: s1, lo: s2);
383}

386/*********** Multiplications ************/
387/* double-double = double * double */
388static inline double2
389dd_mul_d_d(double a, double b)
390{
391 double p, e;
392 p = two_prod(a, b, err: &e);
393 return dd_create(hi: p, lo: e);
394}
395
396/* double-double * double, where double is a power of 2. */
397static inline double2
398dd_mul_pwr2(const double2 a, double b)
399{
400 return dd_create(hi: a.x[0] * b, lo: a.x[1] * b);
401}
402
403static inline double2
404dd_mul(const double2 a, const double2 b)
405{
406 double p1, p2;
407 p1 = two_prod(a: a.x[0], b: b.x[0], err: &p2);
408 p2 += (a.x[0] * b.x[1] + a.x[1] * b.x[0]);
409 p1 = quick_two_sum(a: p1, b: p2, err: &p2);
410 return dd_create(hi: p1, lo: p2);
411}
412
413static inline double2
414dd_mul_dd_d(const double2 a, double b)
415{
416 double p1, p2, e1, e2;
417 p1 = two_prod(a: a.x[0], b, err: &e1);
418 p2 = two_prod(a: a.x[1], b, err: &e2);
419 p1 = quick_two_sum(a: p1, b: e2 + p2 + e1, err: &e1);
420 return dd_create(hi: p1, lo: e1);
421}
422
423static inline double2
424dd_mul_d_dd(double a, const double2 b)
425{
426 double p1, p2, e1, e2;
427 p1 = two_prod(a, b: b.x[0], err: &e1);
428 p2 = two_prod(a, b: b.x[1], err: &e2);
429 p1 = quick_two_sum(a: p1, b: e2 + p2 + e1, err: &e1);
430 return dd_create(hi: p1, lo: e1);
431}

434/*********** Divisions ************/
435static inline double2
436dd_sloppy_div(const double2 a, const double2 b)
437{
438 double s1, s2;
439 double q1, q2;
440 double2 r;
441
442 q1 = a.x[0] / b.x[0]; /* approximate quotient */
443
444 /* compute this - q1 * dd */
445 r = dd_sub(a, b: dd_mul_dd_d(a: b, b: q1));
446 s1 = two_diff(a: a.x[0], b: r.x[0], err: &s2);
447 s2 -= r.x[1];
448 s2 += a.x[1];
449
450 /* get next approximation */
451 q2 = (s1 + s2) / b.x[0];
452
453 /* renormalize */
454 r.x[0] = quick_two_sum(a: q1, b: q2, err: &r.x[1]);
455 return r;
456}
457
458static inline double2
459dd_accurate_div(const double2 a, const double2 b)
460{
461 double q1, q2, q3;
462 double2 r;
463
464 q1 = a.x[0] / b.x[0]; /* approximate quotient */
465
466 r = dd_sub(a, b: dd_mul_dd_d(a: b, b: q1));
467
468 q2 = r.x[0] / b.x[0];
469 r = dd_sub(a: r, b: dd_mul_dd_d(a: b, b: q2));
470
471 q3 = r.x[0] / b.x[0];
472
473 q1 = quick_two_sum(a: q1, b: q2, err: &q2);
474 r = dd_add_dd_d(a: dd_create(hi: q1, lo: q2), b: q3);
475 return r;
476}
477
478static inline double2
479dd_div(const double2 a, const double2 b)
480{
481 return dd_accurate_div(a, b);
482}
483
484static inline double2
485dd_div_d_d(double a, double b)
486{
487 return dd_accurate_div(a: dd_create_d(hi: a), b: dd_create_d(hi: b));
488}
489
490static inline double2
491dd_div_dd_d(const double2 a, double b)
492{
493 return dd_accurate_div(a, b: dd_create_d(hi: b));
494}
495
496static inline double2
497dd_div_d_dd(double a, const double2 b)
498{
499 return dd_accurate_div(a: dd_create_d(hi: a), b);
500}

502static inline double2
503dd_inv(const double2 a)
504{
505 return dd_div(a: DD_C_ONE, b: a);
506}

509/********** Remainder **********/
510static inline double2
511dd_drem(const double2 a, const double2 b)
512{
513 double2 n = dd_nint(a: dd_div(a, b));
514 return dd_sub(a, b: dd_mul(a: n, b));
515}
516
517static inline double2
518dd_divrem(const double2 a, const double2 b, double2 *r)
519{
520 double2 n = dd_nint(a: dd_div(a, b));
521 *r = dd_sub(a, b: dd_mul(a: n, b));
522 return n;
523}
524
525static inline double2
526dd_fmod(const double2 a, const double2 b)
527{
528 double2 n = dd_aint(a: dd_div(a, b));
529 return dd_sub(a, b: dd_mul(a: b, b: n));
530}
531
532/*********** Squaring **********/
533static inline double2
534dd_sqr(const double2 a)
535{
536 double p1, p2;
537 double s1, s2;
538 p1 = two_sqr(a: a.x[0], err: &p2);
539 p2 += 2.0 * a.x[0] * a.x[1];
540 p2 += a.x[1] * a.x[1];
541 s1 = quick_two_sum(a: p1, b: p2, err: &s2);
542 return dd_create(hi: s1, lo: s2);
543}
544
545static inline double2
546dd_sqr_d(double a)
547{
548 double p1, p2;
549 p1 = two_sqr(a, err: &p2);
550 return dd_create(hi: p1, lo: p2);
551}
